</taxonomicName>
differs from all congeners by having the following characters: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,356,1823,1849]" pageId="17" pageNumber="84">
<taxonomicName box="[151,253,1823,1848]" class="Reptilia" family="Agamidae" genus="Sitana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="17" pageNumber="84" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bahiri" status="sp. nov.">
