</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[263,356,1824,1849]" pageId="17" pageNumber="84" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
: snout longer ES 
<number box="[569,683,1824,1849]" pageId="17" pageNumber="84" value="64.8" valueMax="68.1" valueMin="61.5">61.5–68.1</number>
% of HW (vs. shorter, ES 
